Package: WRSVMr
Type: Package
Title: Weighted Relaxed Support Vector Machine for Multiclass Classification
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Annice", "Najafi", email = "annicenajafi27@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Talayeh", "Razzaghi", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides four decomposition strategies (Crammer-Singer, SimMSVM,
    One-vs-One, One-vs-Rest) crossed with four formulations (SVM, RSVM,
    WSVM, WRSVM) for multiclass classification under class imbalance and
    label noise. Wraps the Python wrsvm package via reticulate.
